comments.body:
`SetHexDeprecated()` was recently removed in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/32237

Possible resolution here:
```
                   auto opt_hash = uint256::FromHex(hash_arr[i].get_str());
                     if (!opt_hash) {


                         BOOST_ERROR("Bad test: Invalid hex string" << strTest);
                         continue;
                     }
                     hash.push_back(*opt_hash);
```

